1.0.1.1 Description

Dataset name: Raw data for Study 1

This is the raw dataset for study 1 that will be used as input for the pre-processing script. Since this data is not yet preprocessed, and many of the variables are directly created by jspsych, the variables may not be immediately interpretable or relevant.
